    "_scoring_notes": "Scoring:A score for each social support subscale can be computed as either a total score or an average for the individual items. Higher scores indicate more support.Emotional/informational support: items 2, 3, 7, 8, 12, 15, 16, 18Tangible support: items 1, 4, 11, 14Affectionate support: items 5, 9, 19Positive social interaction: items 6, 10, 17",
